Run script to produce trailer-menu xml file.
./fetch-trailers.pl /usr/local/share/mythtv/themes/defaultmenu/hdmovietrailers.xml

Add button to invoke it to some menu file like so:

<button>
      <type>MOVIETIMES</type>
      <text>Movie Trailers</text>
      <action>MENU hdmovietrailers.xml</action>
</button>
